{"tid":2058443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武係要保護自己，唔需要保護和理非。","createTime":"2020-06-10T07:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T23:24:47.000Z","uid":113155,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a28a58b2edd51b9361eac203b0e4b144b2134812","tid":2058443,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1395242620783936/posts/2336542559987266/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1395242620783936%2Fposts%2F2336542559987266%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=9bcb7466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1395242620783936/posts/2336542559987266/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武手足成身傷，其中有為保護和理非而受傷。<br />\n勇武保護好自己，和理非而家出到去都預48，咩都冇拉到先安全，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有咩事勇武其實要走先</span></span>，連鐳射筆都入到，仲有咩入唔到？<br />\n<br />\n和勇合一：<br />\n勇武：和理非咩都冇，我要保護佢哋走先。（唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n和理非：多一個和理非被捕，就多一個勇武走甩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武拉一個少一個，好好照顧自己。</span></span>和理非拉完可以再出黎，有個被捕師，被捕19次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d6e3166f82e39a0b083e08c34356808d923326","tid":2058443,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fa34bb409ceb2915dcb7c721b4dd00b99b16728","tid":2058443,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053cfe05452988952f62189bc2ed2bbdf224f98a","tid":2058443,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"真係要做野既唔會見到留到最後,屠龍都唔係衰係戀戰度<img src=\"/